News.Title: E-Factor Experiences Wins ₹23.60 Crore EPC Contract for Ecotourism Project
News.Summary: E-Factor Experiences has secured an Engineering, Procurement, and Construction (EPC) contract worth ₹23.60 crore for an ecotourism project in Nongkhyllem Wildlife Sanctuary, Meghalaya. This contract highlights the company's involvement in sustainable tourism development and infrastructure projects in ecologically sensitive areas.
